Sentencas: The Pr1-xSrCoO3-delta perovskite-type oxides have received extensive attention as a promising cathode material due to their favorable properties for realizing high performance intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This study focuses on the electrical properties, electrochemical performance, and redox behavior of a perovskite oxide of Pr1-xSrxCoO3-delta (x = 0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7).
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For x= 0.1 and 0.3, the electrical conductivities increase with increasing strontium content.
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the case of x > 0.3, however, decreased electrical conductivity is observed with increasing x.
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The oxygen non-stoichiometry of Pr1-xSrxCoO3-delta using coulometric titration and its electrical conductivity in a wide range of oxygen partial pressure at 973 K are also investigated.
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A Ni-GDC anode-supported cell is fabricated to evaluate the electrochemical performance of the Pr1-xSrxCoO3-delta cathode material.
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density at 973 K is 1.19 W cm(-2) for x= 0.3, and the other samples also show high power density over 1.0 W cm-2, except for at x= 0.7.
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Given its high electrical conductivity and cell performance, Pr0.7Sr0.3CoO3-delta is a favorable cathode material candidate for IT-SOFC applications.
Titulo: Electrochemical investigation of strontium doping effect on high performance Pr1-xSrxCoO3-δ (x=0.1, 0.3, 0.5, and 0.7) cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
